    Class Description
    Arduino
    Establishes a connection with the Arduino-Board and provides methods to send commands to control the car.

    The Cam Class is used to set the settings, initialized the cam, the socket and the preview.
    CameraPreview  
    CameraSurface  
    Connection
    Provides an API for handling and changing connection data.
    Controller_Android
    Wraps all other classes into this class to be used by the activity.
    GPS
    Provides an API for handling GPS data.
    MyPreviewCallback  
    Network
    This class is used to start the connection with the pc-programm.
    Record_Sound
    Used to record audio and save it to the sdcard.
    Socket_Controller
    This class is used for receiving data from the pc to control the application
    Socket_Package
    This class is used to send information to the PC
    Sound
    Provides methods to load Soundfiles into RAM and play then.
